      <title>2013-05-24 《小豆豆的童年》读书笔记</title>
      <link>https://huizhixu.github.io/chs/life/20130524-%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%86%E8%B1%86%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</link>
